verbose_text: However, in the BRD4 / JMJD6 complex, the JMJD6 linear peptide retains a helical conformation similar to that observed in the full JMJD6 protein (helix alpha6) and interacts with the BRD4 ET three-helix bundle.71 Of note is that in contrast to other cases, the JMJD6 small interacting peptide is not embedded within flexible linkers, but is included into a well folded domain.
